fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.codegen

Class MapGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.codegen.MapGenerator

  • public class MapGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Code generator for Map objects. This object mirrors the interface of Map but instead provides methods for generating usages of Map's interface. This allows changes in Map's interface to be encapsulated.
